{"tid":2487996,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉天橋擲蓋襲警 被告稱拉錯人","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:53:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d52c7d32135cca5c5b399ee7cf69bc2c004fd164","tid":2487996,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/LL7KHK77SFHAFFL2WYEVVWTRUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FLL7KHK77SFHAFFL2WYEVVWTRUI%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11HjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=4d3b3e7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FLL7KHK77SFHAFFL2WYEVVWTRUI%2F&h=1a68786a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/LL7KHK77SFHAFFL2WYEVVWTRUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n涉天橋擲蓋襲警 被告稱拉錯人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/577-NW-S4bmLrtUFvkEKGofX5Fk=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KBRJ3LLMJBAJZJEMTMLIBPGGZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F577-NW-S4bmLrtUFvkEKGofX5Fk%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKBRJ3LLMJBAJZJEMTMLIBPGGZQ.jpg&h=8e9c977a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁文輝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前年10月1日全港多處爆發衝突，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人梁文輝（圖）的代表大狀指，首名警員的口供稱，當日在橋底看到橋上戴有頭盔、黑白泳鏡和黑衣裝束的人士掟下垃圾桶後，他才跑上樓梯追捕，其間有10秒目光離開目標人物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「倘戴頭盔不會受傷」<br />\n<br />\n大狀認為橋上有多名身穿黑衫黑褲人士，質疑警員是隨便將差不多裝束的梁拘捕，直指警方拉錯人。<br />\n<br />\n大狀又指，若真如警方證人所指，梁當時一直戴有頭盔，便不可能造成頭頂兩道撕裂傷勢，頭盔更不可能沒沾上血迹。律政司代表回應稱，戴頭盔與否並非重點，梁被認出掟垃圾桶蓋才是重點。張官不同意：「點會唔係重點？𠵱家就係拗有冇疑點吖嘛！」並指若梁當時根本沒戴頭盔，即代表警察口供有問題。<br />\n<br />\n控方又稱警員制服梁時，注意力不在頭盔上，並稱梁當時或是在掙扎下甩掉頭盔。張官聞言指，控方責任是要證明定罪沒合理疑點，「有可能甩咗」此類說法非控方應有的恰當論點。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCMA371/20"},{"pid":"e0a935d3e9ceeeb5a4f9771accf2733fca06363a","tid":2487996,"uid":256330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:53:08.000Z","msg":"有罪推論啊依家？律政司個堆係咪都係毅進仔？"}]}